HEADWORD: Gome
<hw>Gome</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>guma</ets>;
akin to Goth. <ets>guma</ets>, L. <ets>homo</ets>. See
<er>Bridegroom</er>.]</ety> <def>A man.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>P. Plowman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
