==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Gome
<hw>Gome</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Icel. <ets>gormr</ets> ooze,
mud.]</ety> <def>The black grease on the axle of a cart or wagon wheel;
-- called also <altname>gorm</altname>. See <er>Gorm</er>.</def>
<mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gomer</ent>⟦br⟧
